1
00:00:07,730 --> 00:00:09,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He still isn't awake yet?</font>

2
00:00:12,950 --> 00:00:15,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This whole thing is such a mess.</font>

3
00:00:15,610 --> 00:00:18,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will raise this child by myself.</font>

4
00:00:18,030 --> 00:00:20,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know that I can make 
him into a magician.</font>

5
00:00:20,810 --> 00:00:25,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">None of us have any idea when that boy 
may transform into The End of All Things.</font>

6
00:00:26,210 --> 00:00:30,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I believe in Luna. I believe in her.</i></font>

7
00:00:32,380 --> 00:00:34,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I meant to ask you.</font>

8
00:00:34,570 --> 00:00:37,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That Cat Witch that 
appeared the other day.</font>

9
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:39,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She was a friend of yours?</font>

10
00:02:18,380 --> 00:02:24,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This story happened before the black 
cat Sisi came to live in Luna's house.</i></font>

11
00:02:27,420 --> 00:02:30,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look. Isn't that her?</font>

12
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:32,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The one who moved to the forest</font>

13
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:36,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EPISODE 5: I CANNOT RETURN
 TO THE CAT FOREST</font>

14
00:02:32,470 --> 00:02:35,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and got a special exemption 
to become a black witch?</font>

15
00:02:35,500 --> 00:02:38,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Champignon Witch, Luna?</font>

16
00:02:38,990 --> 00:02:45,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ew, look! Everything she steps on or 
touches really does grow mushrooms!</font>

17
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:51,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Dorothy! If we're here to spy on 
her, could you at least keep it down?</font>

18
00:02:51,730 --> 00:02:53,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ew, that's so gross!</font>

19
00:02:53,980 --> 00:02:56,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you even listening to me, Dorothy?</font>

20
00:02:56,190 --> 00:02:59,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't have to tell me, Bat Magician.</font>

21
00:02:59,870 --> 00:03:03,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're here as representatives 
of the black witches</font>

22
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:06,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to spy on the shady new girl.</font>

23
00:03:08,500 --> 00:03:11,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, hey! A real weirdo moved in nearby!</font>

24
00:03:11,750 --> 00:03:14,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Imagine the nerve! Let's go find her!</font>

25
00:03:15,580 --> 00:03:18,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How are we representatives 
when nobody asked us to come?</font>

26
00:03:19,210 --> 00:03:22,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about you shut up, Mouse Magician!</font>

27
00:03:22,380 --> 00:03:23,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hiss!</font>

28
00:03:23,530 --> 00:03:27,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}SECOND-RATE BULLY</font>

29
00:03:23,690 --> 00:03:25,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I just wanna go home.</i></font>

30
00:03:24,620 --> 00:03:27,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}PICKS ON THE WEAK</font>

31
00:03:25,020 --> 00:03:27,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You're the one who needs to shut up.</i></font>

32
00:03:27,140 --> 00:03:32,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We use our magic to help 
cleanse this poisoned world</i></font>

33
00:03:32,350 --> 00:03:34,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and protect it from behind the scenes.</i></font>

34
00:03:34,870 --> 00:03:38,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We are proud black witches 
and black magicians.</i></font>

35
00:03:38,660 --> 00:03:39,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In training, you mean.</font>

36
00:03:39,690 --> 00:03:42,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll be official soon enough!</font>

37
00:03:42,030 --> 00:03:44,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But that Champignon Witch,</font>

38
00:03:44,180 --> 00:03:48,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard she became a black witch 
with almost no real training.</font>

39
00:03:48,650 --> 00:03:50,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How was she able to pull that off?</font>

40
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:52,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're just jealous.</font>

41
00:03:52,290 --> 00:03:54,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's way too fishy to be legit.</font>

42
00:03:54,740 --> 00:03:58,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And just look at that! She's 
already noticed we're here!</font>

43
00:03:59,220 --> 00:04:03,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dang it! All because you guys couldn't 
keep your mouths shut! Get down!</font>

44
00:04:03,100 --> 00:04:06,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the one who's been 
doing all the yapping.</font>

45
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:11,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder if all the rumors are true.</font>

46
00:04:11,740 --> 00:04:12,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rumors?</font>

47
00:04:13,980 --> 00:04:17,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">About her. That she used 
to be a cursed youngling.</font>

48
00:04:17,300 --> 00:04:17,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

49
00:04:17,790 --> 00:04:19,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks to the magic she was born with,</font>

50
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:22,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">she didn't become The End of All Things.</font>

51
00:04:22,030 --> 00:04:23,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She was a cursed youngling?</i></font>

52
00:04:24,330 --> 00:04:27,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It made her breath and body poisonous.</font>

53
00:04:27,390 --> 00:04:30,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The mushrooms she grows 
are all poisonous, too.</font>

54
00:04:30,580 --> 00:04:36,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ew! That's so nasty! Gross! 
Why is she even here?!</font>

55
00:04:34,840 --> 00:04:36,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Shh! Shh!</font>

56
00:04:36,510 --> 00:04:39,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Mmfh! Mmph!</font>

57
00:04:38,220 --> 00:04:45,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, our cover is so far blown, I 
think she's started making tea for us.</font>

58
00:04:48,650 --> 00:04:54,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is a disaster. To think that such 
a creepy girl is a black witch like us.</i></font>

59
00:04:54,150 --> 00:04:56,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's gonna give all of us 
black witches a bad name!</i></font>

60
00:04:56,940 --> 00:05:02,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We have nothing to do with her, but the 
humans aren't gonna know the difference!</i></font>

61
00:05:03,400 --> 00:05:09,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I heard our master, the Beast 
Magician, is taking good care of her.</font>

62
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:12,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe we could also be... 
uh, maybe not <i>friendly</i>,</font>

63
00:05:12,650 --> 00:05:15,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but why don't we back off 
and give her some space?</font>

64
00:05:17,650 --> 00:05:19,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did you just say?</font>

65
00:05:19,500 --> 00:05:21,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She gets tons of attention only 
because she's such a pain in the neck,</font>

66
00:05:21,960 --> 00:05:23,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and gets private lessons from our master 
when she's not even his apprentice?!</font>

67
00:05:23,900 --> 00:05:27,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's backed our poor master into a corner
 where he has to waste all his time</font>

68
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:31,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">rehabilitating this delinquent instead 
of tutoring his top students?!</font>

69
00:05:31,230 --> 00:05:33,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Jealousy, check. Resentment, check.</i></font>

70
00:05:33,130 --> 00:05:35,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Talk about biased commentary.</i></font>

71
00:05:36,520 --> 00:05:40,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's unbelievable. I'll never 
forgive her for this, damn it!</font>

72
00:05:40,730 --> 00:05:44,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why'd you have to bring 
up the master, man?</font>

73
00:05:44,170 --> 00:05:45,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My bad.</font>

74
00:05:52,080 --> 00:05:56,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's no way to serve tea to a guest! 
Where the hell are your manners?</font>

75
00:05:56,580 --> 00:06:00,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll bully her until she runs crying 
from the black witch community!</i></font>

76
00:06:10,840 --> 00:06:11,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Uh...</i></font>

77
00:06:12,590 --> 00:06:14,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How did we end up in here?</i></font>

78
00:06:16,100 --> 00:06:19,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You're the one who doesn't 
have any manners.</i></font>

79
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:24,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't this great, Luna? I know you said 
you wanted try a tea party for once,</font>

80
00:06:24,900 --> 00:06:28,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">just like the one you read about 
in that book the other day.</font>

81
00:06:29,410 --> 00:06:30,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What?</i></font>

82
00:06:32,260 --> 00:06:35,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oops. I'm not gonna let something 
like that make me lower my guard.</i></font>

83
00:06:37,420 --> 00:06:41,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You baked these with those 
poison hands of yours, right?</font>

84
00:06:41,250 --> 00:06:44,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Scary! There's no way I could eat one.</font>

85
00:06:44,330 --> 00:06:46,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wow, she's terrible.</i></font>

86
00:06:46,380 --> 00:06:50,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't this great, Luna? Finally, 
a chance to talk to people!</font>

87
00:06:50,010 --> 00:06:51,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, don't be shy.</font>

88
00:06:52,280 --> 00:06:54,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Uh, what?</i></font>

89
00:06:54,070 --> 00:06:57,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nobody was even willing to 
get close to you before!</font>

90
00:06:58,920 --> 00:07:02,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She must be so miserable she can't 
even tell when she's being picked on.</i></font>

91
00:07:02,780 --> 00:07:07,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She didn't touch the cookies with her 
bare hands, so they're okay to eat.</font>

92
00:07:08,350 --> 00:07:10,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're even learning about 
good manners today.</font>

93
00:07:13,530 --> 00:07:17,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't you glad our first 
guests are such nice people?</font>

94
00:07:17,660 --> 00:07:20,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is such a wonderful day.</font>

95
00:07:20,840 --> 00:07:23,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know, I could eat 
this for you if you want.</font>

96
00:07:30,910 --> 00:07:33,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Cat Witch was perplexed.</i></font>

97
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:36,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You could say that her toxic 
attitude had been washed away,</i></font>

98
00:07:36,970 --> 00:07:39,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>defenseless against this 
sudden shower of goodwill.</i></font>

99
00:07:40,370 --> 00:07:43,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The cruelty she was so used to flaunting</i></font>

100
00:07:43,160 --> 00:07:45,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>could not find suitable footing</i></font>

101
00:07:45,590 --> 00:07:50,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>in an atmosphere drenched with such 
a profound sense of loneliness,</i></font>

102
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:54,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and that seemed to have 
thrown her off her game...</i></font>

103
00:07:56,610 --> 00:08:00,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>especially because she had 
never once associated herself</i></font>

104
00:08:00,200 --> 00:08:03,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>with the words "nice people" 
before in her life.</i></font>

105
00:08:04,210 --> 00:08:06,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here comes that black witch again.</font>

106
00:08:06,940 --> 00:08:09,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She goes around feeding all 
those thieving stray cats.</font>

107
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:12,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're so noisy at night!</font>

108
00:08:12,070 --> 00:08:15,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She isn't even helping us 
get rid of all the mice!</font>

109
00:08:16,860 --> 00:08:21,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's all your fault, you know! 
I had to cut back on the mousetraps</font>

110
00:08:21,350 --> 00:08:23,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">with you around, so now I get blamed!</font>

111
00:08:23,440 --> 00:08:25,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Grr.</font>

112
00:08:26,110 --> 00:08:30,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's he gonna do? It's not like 
he can do his job without familiars.</font>

113
00:08:26,440 --> 00:08:27,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hiss!</font>

114
00:08:30,850 --> 00:08:35,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And we can't do our job gathering info 
if we don't get along with the townsfolk.</font>

115
00:08:35,690 --> 00:08:37,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for being so considerate.</font>

116
00:08:37,910 --> 00:08:39,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's hard enough here already,</font>

117
00:08:39,470 --> 00:08:42,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">where black witches have 
such a bad reputation.</font>

118
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey. Isn't that...</font>

119
00:08:50,650 --> 00:08:54,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you must be the mushroom 
witch I keep hearing about.</font>

120
00:08:54,670 --> 00:08:57,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Recently I have noticed a suspi... uh,</font>

121
00:08:57,030 --> 00:09:00,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">a very inquisitive-looking person
 passing by the store.</font>

122
00:09:00,760 --> 00:09:03,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you were friends with 
the Cat Witch all along?</font>

123
00:09:04,420 --> 00:09:06,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wouldn't say we're friends or anything.</font>

124
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:09,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She is a little hard to 
get along with, though.</font>

125
00:09:10,100 --> 00:09:12,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Has she been picking on you at all?</font>

126
00:09:12,690 --> 00:09:13,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hiss!</font>

127
00:09:14,100 --> 00:09:17,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's your own fault! Ow, ow, ouch!</font>

128
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:19,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She isn't like that at all.</font>

129
00:09:20,260 --> 00:09:21,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She talks!</font>

130
00:09:21,390 --> 00:09:22,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

131
00:09:22,570 --> 00:09:24,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She is a wonderful individual.</font>

132
00:09:25,310 --> 00:09:29,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks to her, I finally got 
to visit this bookstore today.</font>

133
00:09:30,150 --> 00:09:34,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She keeps doing nice things for me. 
I think she is a very kind person.</font>

134
00:09:37,230 --> 00:09:42,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh. "Kind" isn't a word that comes 
to mind when I think of the Cat Witch.</font>

135
00:09:44,020 --> 00:09:47,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Starting around then, whenever the 
Cat Witch was showered in compliments</i></font>

136
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:50,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>such as "kind" or "nice,"</i></font>

137
00:09:50,760 --> 00:09:52,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>she'd get a blissful 
expression on her face,</i></font>

138
00:09:52,930 --> 00:09:56,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>as if she was under some kind of spell.</i></font>

139
00:09:57,740 --> 00:10:00,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In time, she started to visit 
the mushroom house more often</i></font>

140
00:10:01,280 --> 00:10:05,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>in order to get another helping of 
this new and still unfamiliar feeling.</i></font>

141
00:10:06,470 --> 00:10:10,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Luna, aren't you glad she's lending 
you the book you wanted to read?</font>

142
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:15,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The birds in town were singing, "the 
Cat Witch has a twisted, evil soul,"</font>

143
00:10:15,870 --> 00:10:18,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but that isn't true at all, is it?</font>

144
00:10:18,220 --> 00:10:21,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's a kind witch, and she's been 
coming to visit us a bunch recently,</font>

145
00:10:21,530 --> 00:10:24,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so every day has been lots of fun.</font>

146
00:10:24,420 --> 00:10:26,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It was as if these 
unadulterated showers of praise</i></font>

147
00:10:26,980 --> 00:10:31,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>yanked the teeth out of 
the witch's cruel bite.</i></font>

148
00:10:56,910 --> 00:11:01,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure, Luna has a poison body because 
she was once a cursed youngling,</font>

149
00:11:01,430 --> 00:11:05,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but it's also because she absorbs 
and cleans poison from the world.</font>

150
00:11:05,310 --> 00:11:06,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you know that?</font>

151
00:11:06,430 --> 00:11:11,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All these people who talk trash about 
her don't even care. It's unbelievable!</font>

152
00:11:11,800 --> 00:11:15,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're the worst! They don't
even try to get to know her.</font>

153
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:19,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She should try saying all 
this to her old self.</font>

154
00:11:19,070 --> 00:11:22,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's more likely to cast a spell 
to forget her bad behavior.</font>

155
00:11:24,920 --> 00:11:29,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Before, all the trees and animals of this 
black forest were contaminated with poison</font>

156
00:11:29,210 --> 00:11:32,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and it was home to all sorts 
of pests and evil spirits.</font>

157
00:11:32,130 --> 00:11:34,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But once you moved here,</font>

158
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:37,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it changed from a black forest 
to a poison mushroom forest.</font>

159
00:11:37,060 --> 00:11:39,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can feel safe letting 
my cats play here now.</font>

160
00:11:40,290 --> 00:11:44,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, it sounds kind of impersonal 
when you call me "Miss Dorothy."</font>

161
00:11:44,550 --> 00:11:46,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just call me "Dorothy" 
as if I was your sister.</font>

162
00:11:46,780 --> 00:11:48,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Well, that came out of nowhere.</i></font>

163
00:11:49,220 --> 00:11:55,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... Dor... Sis... Miss Witch? Um...</font>

164
00:11:55,440 --> 00:11:58,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, this is what happens with someone 
who's not comfortable with people.</font>

165
00:11:59,420 --> 00:12:02,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you tell me why you decided 
to become a cat witch?</font>

166
00:12:03,640 --> 00:12:07,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's simple. Obviously 
because I love cats so much!</font>

167
00:12:07,390 --> 00:12:09,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wasn't it the same for you,
 with mushrooms?</font>

168
00:12:11,210 --> 00:12:15,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is such a nice place, 
though. But did you know?</font>

169
00:12:15,610 --> 00:12:19,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They say there's also a legendary 
cat forest that only cats live in.</font>

170
00:12:19,780 --> 00:12:24,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sometimes, the more distinguished cat 
witches even get invitations to visit.</font>

171
00:12:24,510 --> 00:12:26,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A cat forest...</i></font>

172
00:12:26,710 --> 00:12:31,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really want to go see it myself, but 
I guess because I'm still inexperienced,</font>

173
00:12:31,310 --> 00:12:34,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the forest's chief won't
 give me permission.</font>

174
00:12:34,410 --> 00:12:37,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shucks, why am I not good enough?</font>

175
00:12:37,700 --> 00:12:41,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dorothy? Not her. Furr-get it. 
She's hiss-terically loud.</font>

176
00:12:41,790 --> 00:12:44,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's a blabber-meowth. A real purr-oblem.</font>

177
00:12:43,370 --> 00:12:45,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I see what you mean meow.</font>

178
00:12:45,180 --> 00:12:51,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I can imagine what it's like 
from what these guys have told me.</font>

179
00:12:51,320 --> 00:12:53,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Almost like I've been there before.</font>

180
00:12:53,610 --> 00:12:58,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In fact, I bet I used to live 
there as a cat in a past life.</font>

181
00:12:58,020 --> 00:13:01,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, I hope I can visit
 the cat forest soon.</font>

182
00:13:01,550 --> 00:13:03,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know what my dream in life is?</font>

183
00:13:03,190 --> 00:13:08,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's to put this silly, poisoned world 
behind me, move to the cat forest</font>

184
00:13:08,770 --> 00:13:13,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">where nobody hassles me and 
I can be with the cats I love</font>

185
00:13:13,080 --> 00:13:16,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and live there happily ever after.</font>

186
00:13:16,770 --> 00:13:21,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, that was what I always wanted, 
until I met this Champignon Witch,</font>

187
00:13:21,420 --> 00:13:24,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who fights so bravely to 
rid the world of poison.</font>

188
00:13:25,380 --> 00:13:28,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now that I've seen how pretty 
the black forest has become,</font>

189
00:13:28,590 --> 00:13:31,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">as your big sister and 
senior as a black witch,</font>

190
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:33,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can see I still have 
a lot of work to do.</font>

191
00:13:35,580 --> 00:13:39,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}That said, our job is actually espionage.</font>

192
00:13:36,050 --> 00:13:38,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The cat forest. A homeland 
she has not yet seen.</i></font>

193
00:13:39,460 --> 00:13:40,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Espionage?</font>

194
00:13:39,460 --> 00:13:43,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But she cannot return to 
the cat forest just yet.</i></font>

195
00:13:40,760 --> 00:13:47,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Cats aren't poisonous animals, so instead 
of purifying like poison witches...</font>

196
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:52,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dorothy, the tabby who got 
into the white witch's castle</font>

197
00:13:52,310 --> 00:13:54,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">has been missing for two days meow!</font>

198
00:13:54,180 --> 00:13:55,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet mew they caught her!</font>

199
00:13:55,800 --> 00:13:57,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How many does that make meow?</font>

200
00:13:57,740 --> 00:13:58,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What meow?</font>

201
00:13:58,940 --> 00:14:00,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now what do we mew?</font>

202
00:14:03,250 --> 00:14:07,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The tabby's dead fur sure! There's 
no point trying to save him meow!</font>

203
00:14:07,820 --> 00:14:09,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We don't know for sure yet.</font>

204
00:14:09,570 --> 00:14:12,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But either way, if they 
suspect us of spying now,</font>

205
00:14:12,580 --> 00:14:16,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">all of the cats and I are 
in danger of being purged!</font>

206
00:14:16,330 --> 00:14:21,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's also several black witches in the 
castle who are being unjustly detained!</font>

207
00:14:22,340 --> 00:14:24,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sisi, you guys need to get away!</font>

208
00:14:24,970 --> 00:14:28,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go tell the master and our 
friends what's happening here!</font>

209
00:14:29,510 --> 00:14:32,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll use the confusion 
to sneak into the castle,</font>

210
00:14:32,320 --> 00:14:37,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">rescue the tabby and other cats, and give
 the white witches a little surprise!</font>

211
00:14:39,020 --> 00:14:40,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, Dorothy! It's too dangerous!</font>

212
00:14:40,850 --> 00:14:43,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to distract them 
so everyone can get away.</font>

213
00:14:43,770 --> 00:14:47,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be all right, Sisi. I'm not afraid.</font>

214
00:14:47,910 --> 00:14:49,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I remember what she said...</font>

215
00:14:49,860 --> 00:14:51,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She is a very kind person.</i></font>

216
00:14:51,400 --> 00:14:55,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It makes me want to live up to
 those words, and protect everyone I can.</i></font>

217
00:14:57,310 --> 00:14:59,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to collect every bit
 of this strange feeling,</i></font>

218
00:14:59,930 --> 00:15:03,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and clutch it tight, close to my heart.</i></font>

219
00:15:04,460 --> 00:15:10,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't want to return to the cat forest 
until I've truly become that person.</i></font>

220
00:15:39,740 --> 00:15:43,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the town square where 
Dorothy was executed the other day.</font>

221
00:15:45,000 --> 00:15:48,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for coming, Champignon Witch.</font>

222
00:15:48,680 --> 00:15:51,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mouse Magician...</font>

223
00:15:51,010 --> 00:15:54,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry to show up like this, 
but I need to stay undercover.</font>

224
00:16:08,590 --> 00:16:12,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The ground here is stained 
with the Cat Witch's</i></font>

225
00:16:12,610 --> 00:16:18,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>grief mushroom, pain mushroom,
 anger mushroom,</i></font>

226
00:16:18,790 --> 00:16:24,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>fear mushroom, misery mushroom, 
solitude mushroom...</i></font>

227
00:16:24,620 --> 00:16:32,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look, Sisi. All of Dorothy's pain is 
growing into mushrooms to be cleansed.</font>

228
00:16:46,130 --> 00:16:47,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kindness mushrooms?</font>

229
00:16:54,620 --> 00:16:57,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, come on. Stop crying, okay?</font>

230
00:17:00,910 --> 00:17:02,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bye now!</font>

231
00:17:08,420 --> 00:17:14,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Luna, these guys are saying that
 the Cat Witch is in the cat forest now.</font>

232
00:17:27,830 --> 00:17:30,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I believe in Luna.</i></font>

233
00:17:31,370 --> 00:17:32,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I believe in her.</i></font>

234
00:17:47,110 --> 00:17:48,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My darling Noah.</i></font>

235
00:17:55,390 --> 00:17:58,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Please, hurry and die for me.</i></font>

236
00:18:00,470 --> 00:18:03,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You will never be allowed 
to be reborn again.</i></font>

237
00:18:05,980 --> 00:18:07,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>For the sake of this country,</i></font>

238
00:18:08,310 --> 00:18:11,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>indeed, for the sake of this world...</i></font>

239
00:18:24,420 --> 00:18:28,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are the one who should 
never have been born.</font>

240
00:18:29,400 --> 00:18:35,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eliminating you is a duty
 I inherited from my late sister,</font>

241
00:18:35,000 --> 00:18:36,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who left you in my hands.</font>

242
00:18:36,750 --> 00:18:42,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it is any consolation, I shall 
allow you to pass on in ignorance.</font>

243
00:18:45,480 --> 00:18:47,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mother...</font>

244
00:18:51,340 --> 00:18:52,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why?</i></font>

245
00:18:53,550 --> 00:18:54,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why?</i></font>

246
00:19:05,830 --> 00:19:06,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Who's there?</i></font>

247
00:19:08,410 --> 00:19:13,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Somebody is draining my memories... 
all of the agony from my body?</i></font>

248
00:19:14,440 --> 00:19:20,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Painful memories, depressing 
experiences, dark feelings,</i></font>

249
00:19:21,050 --> 00:19:26,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>whirlpools of uncertainty, constellations 
of suffering, flashbacks of fear,</i></font>

250
00:19:27,170 --> 00:19:29,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and everything illuminated within.</i></font>

251
00:19:30,110 --> 00:19:37,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wait, if you take all of that away, 
I'll barely have any memories left.</i></font>

252
00:19:40,450 --> 00:19:43,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I see. I suppose this shows</i></font>

253
00:19:43,950 --> 00:19:49,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>just how deeply my path in life 
has been stained by sadness.</i></font>

254
00:19:50,920 --> 00:19:52,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's actually beautiful...</i></font>

255
00:19:53,960 --> 00:19:58,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>the light cast by the sadness 
as it flows away from my body.</i></font>

256
00:20:00,340 --> 00:20:01,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No, come back!</i></font>

257
00:20:10,460 --> 00:20:14,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I cannot allow myself to forget 
this one precious memory</i></font>

258
00:20:15,460 --> 00:20:17,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>of the promise I made</i></font>

259
00:20:18,230 --> 00:20:19,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>to my late mother.</i></font>

260
00:20:21,130 --> 00:20:24,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Noah, NoÃ«l, Emile...</font>

261
00:20:26,190 --> 00:20:29,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you have multiple names.</font>

262
00:20:31,160 --> 00:20:33,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He who is destined to be king</font>

263
00:20:33,990 --> 00:20:36,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">must alternate between many 
pseudonyms throughout his life.</font>

264
00:20:38,210 --> 00:20:42,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You absolutely must not reveal 
your true name to anyone.</font>

265
00:20:43,160 --> 00:20:47,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Revealing your true name 
would expose you to a curse.</font>

266
00:20:48,720 --> 00:20:53,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When a king reveals his true name, it 
immediately compromises the throne.</font>

267
00:20:54,740 --> 00:20:59,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When the throne is unstable, it sends 
the country into darkness and confusion.</font>

268
00:21:00,230 --> 00:21:04,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must only recite your true 
name silently, in your mind,</font>

269
00:21:04,680 --> 00:21:06,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">when you need to use your magic.</font>

270
00:21:08,250 --> 00:21:11,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter the curse, if it 
knows not your true name,</font>

271
00:21:11,710 --> 00:21:16,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it can never pose a mortal threat to you.</font>

272
00:21:17,260 --> 00:21:22,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This true name that I have given you is 
one thing that you must never forget.</font>

273
00:21:23,760 --> 00:21:26,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lock it tightly within your heart.</font>

274
00:21:27,820 --> 00:21:29,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your name is...</font>

275
00:21:35,740 --> 00:21:39,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Luna! He just woke up!</font>

276
00:21:39,020 --> 00:21:42,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, who are you? Hey, are you okay?</font>

277
00:21:43,420 --> 00:21:46,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look, you know what you have to do, Luna.</font>

278
00:21:47,550 --> 00:21:50,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What? This is my body?</i></font>

279
00:21:52,540 --> 00:21:55,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Was it always this small?</i></font>

280
00:21:56,700 --> 00:22:00,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What was I like before this?</i></font>

281
00:22:02,050 --> 00:22:07,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These first moments are crucial. If you 
can't make this kid into a magician,</font>

282
00:22:08,380 --> 00:22:10,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he's going to be put down.</font>

283
00:22:11,880 --> 00:22:15,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So set your feelings aside 
and don't cut him any slack.</font>

284
00:22:17,940 --> 00:22:20,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You. Tell us your name.</font>

285
00:22:23,940 --> 00:22:25,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You must never forget</i></font>

286
00:22:26,450 --> 00:22:27,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>that your name is...</i></font>

287
00:22:33,180 --> 00:22:34,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}LIZEL</font>

288
00:22:33,330 --> 00:22:34,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lizel.</font>

